reviewText: MY Grandson loves these videos.  He watches them in the car and they hold his attention.  They are very learning.

My son could not wait to watch these upon arrival. However, it drove me nuts when i played over and over and over again. He loves this set. Also it came so fast i did not even feel like I had to wait. PRovided hours of watching for my son. Girls didn't care for it. But son loves it
